✅ Step 1: WSL enable karo (PowerShell as Admin)
wsl --install

Agar already installed hai, to next step pe jao.

✅ Step 2: Available distros check karo
wsl --list --online

Tumhe list me Ubuntu-22.04 dikh jayega.

✅ Step 3: Ubuntu 22.04 install karo
wsl --install -d Ubuntu-22.04
✅ Step 4: Restart system

Installation ke baad system restart karo (agar bole to).

✅ Step 5: Setup username/password

Restart ke baad Ubuntu open hoga aur bolega:

Enter new UNIX username:
Enter new UNIX password:

Yaha apna username/password set karo.

✅ Step 6: Verify install
lsb_release -a

Output me Ubuntu 22.04 dikhna chahiye.

🔧 Agar issue aaye to

Agar error aaye (common cases):

👉 WSL version update
wsl --update
👉 Default version 2 set karo
wsl --set-default-version 2
💡 Bonus (Useful commands)
wsl -l -v          # installed distros check
wsl --shutdown     # restart WSL
wsl --unregister Ubuntu-22.04   # delete distro
